headline: Walton Global Launches $250 Million Offering Targeting 11.5% Return
summary: SCOTTSDALE, Ariz., July 17, 2025--Walton Global, a real estate investment and land asset management company, has launched Builder Land Finance (BLF) Fund III, a private credit offering designed for accredited investors. The fund offers a land backed, fixed-income opportunity for investors to participate in institutional land banking through flexible financing structures tailored to homebuilder needs.
